      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI < 5% for hemolysis index QoI on production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted per Celik et al. (2008) methodology. GCI for NIH on fine mesh (11.4M cells) is 1.8%, exceeding the required level. Medium mesh (3.8M cells) used for production runs with GCI 4.2%, within acceptance criterion. Achieved level 3 reflects exceedance of MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
