    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate agreement with experimental hemolysis measurements (mean absolute error 8.3%, all within ±20% acceptance band). Worst-case operating condition identified by CFD is consistent with experimental ranking. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at worst-case condition. Six factors scoped out as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The credibility assessment supports use of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
